WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:00.994 --> 00:00:02.668
<i>Previously on "Grimm"...</i>

2
00:00:02.691 --> 00:00:04.640
<i>- A number of Wesen shop owners</i>

3
00:00:04.674 --> 00:00:05.908
<i>were attacked by Wesen last night.</i>

4
00:00:05.942 --> 00:00:07.209
<i>And they're leaving behind a mark.</i>

5
00:00:07.244 --> 00:00:09.078
- Look familiar?
- Black Claw.

6
00:00:09.112 --> 00:00:11.847
<i>And the same people tried
to kill Nick and Monroe.</i>

7
00:00:14.050 --> 00:00:15.918
<i>She just took out 20
Wesen who tried to kill me.</i>

8
00:00:15.952 --> 00:00:17.286
Juliette.

9
00:00:17.320 --> 00:00:18.787
She's alive and you know it!

10
00:00:18.822 --> 00:00:20.356
I didn't know if she was gonna survive

11
00:00:20.390 --> 00:00:22.358
what they were gonna do to her.

12
00:00:22.392 --> 00:00:24.593
<i>The woman you knew
doesn't exist anymore.</i>

13
00:00:24.628 --> 00:00:25.961
<i>What am I supposed to call you?</i>

14
00:00:25.996 --> 00:00:27.363
They call me Eve.

15
00:00:27.397 --> 00:00:28.897
Why did you even agree to meet me here?

16
00:00:33.970 --> 00:00:35.571
What the hell is
this. some kind of test?

17
00:00:35.605 --> 00:00:36.739
I'll be in touch.

18
00:00:38.816 --> 00:00:40.423
__

19
00:00:41.745 --> 00:00:49.718
♪ ♪

20
00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:57.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
